  <section id="Section955801">
    <title><anchor id="Anchor955800" role="Index"
    xreflabel="rescan privileges;privileges:rescanning of" /> <indexterm
        significance="normal" zone="Anchor955800">
        <primary>rescan privileges</primary>
      </indexterm> <indexterm significance="normal" zone="Anchor955800">
        <primary>privileges</primary>

        <secondary>rescanning of</secondary>
      </indexterm>Rescan Privileges</title>

    <para id="Para955802">The Rescan Privileges utility enables a user to
    realize newly-granted privileges without having to log out and log back in
    to the application. To realize newly-granted privileges, simply select the
    "Rescan Privileges" option to execute the utility. The privileges for the
    current user will be rescanned and updated--without the user having to log
    out of the application.</para>
  </section>

